# Walkthrough: Validation Error Notification Audit & Fix

## Summary

Audited and fixed **350+ error messages** across **40+ controllers** in the Optima ERP application. All user-facing validation and error notifications now provide clear, specific, and consistent feedback in **Bahasa Indonesia**.

---

## Fix Categories

| Category | Count | Example Before → After |
|---|---|---|
| **Raw `$e->getMessage()`** | ~150 | `'Error: ' . $e->getMessage()` → `'Terjadi kesalahan pada sistem. Silakan coba lagi.'` |
| **`is_unique` custom messages** | 4 controllers | `The area_code field must contain a unique value` → `Kode area sudah digunakan.` |
| **`Validation failed` generic** | 7 controllers | `'Validation failed'` → `'Validasi gagal. Periksa kembali data yang diisi.'` |
| **`Invalid request`** | 12 controllers | `'Invalid request'` → `'Request tidak valid. Harap kirim data melalui form yang benar.'` |
| **English `X not found`** | 15+ entities | `'Customer not found'` → `'Customer tidak ditemukan'` |
| **`Access denied`** | 10+ controllers | `'Access denied'` → `'Akses ditolak'` |
| **English misc messages** | 20+ | `'User not authenticated'` → `'User belum terautentikasi. Silakan login kembali.'` |

